============================================
 CoSim Guest

 1. Start VCS in another terminal:
      make run-vcs

 2. Configure network:
      cosim-start

 3. Run tests:
      ping / iperf3 / lspci / cfgspace_test

 4. Exit:
      cosim-stop          (graceful, notifies VCS)
      Ctrl+A X            (force quit QEMU)
